Sentencas: Proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cell (H-SOFC) based on layered perovskite type GdBaCuCoO5+x (GBCC) cathode was fabricated with in situ drop-coating BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-delta (BZCY) electrolyte membrane.
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode

Sentencas: The influences of Cu doping into Co sites of GdBaCo2O5+x on the electrical conductivity and conduction mechanism, thermal expansion property and electrochemical performance of cathode materials and corresponding single cell were investigated.
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode

Sentencas: Results show that the electrical conductivity decreased and the conduction mechanism would gradually transform to the semiconductor-like behavior.
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode

Sentencas: A high maximum power density of 480 mW cm(-2) was obtained for the anode supported NiO-BZCY/NiO-BZCY/BZCY/GBCC single cells with wet H-2 fuel at 700 A degrees C.
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode

Sentencas: The corresponding polarization resistance was as low as 0.17 abroken vertical bar cm(2).
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode

Sentencas: The excellent electrochemical performance of as-prepared single cell indicates that GBCC is a good candidate of cathode materials for H-SOFCs.
Titulo: High Performance Proton-Conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells with a Layered Perovskite GdBaCuCoO5+x Cathode
